However, Playboy has expanded its reach over the years and now encompasses a broad range of products and services, including licensing, digital media, consumer products, and entertainment venues. The Playboy Corporation has an estimated net worth of $50 million.

The Gulfstream G650 (GLF6) is a large business jet manufactured by Gulfstream Aerospace , the first customer delivery of this aircraft was in December of 2012. This model can accommodate 11 to 18 passengers, has a range of 8,000 miles, and a cruising speed of 594 mph. A typical Gulfstream G650 costs between 64-70 million dollars, and over 470 individual aircraft have been produced.
